AysnLSTM outputs relevant news headlines (those with high probablity mass) in training the model with two inputs: AAPL time series and daily Thomson Reuters news headlines¶

Follwing cells show all Reuters news headlines from each day of testset (having at least one ground truth news) along with the probablity mass of attention learnt by AsyncLSTM.¶

Headlines with large probablity mass indicates that they are relevant to interpret the given time series, which is AAPL stock prices in this case.¶

Note the company name, Apple, is never given to train AysnLSTM¶
